Package com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.exc

Exception Summary
InvalidFormatException Specialized sub-class of JsonMappingException that is used when the underlying problem appears to be that of bad formatting of a value to deserialize.
UnrecognizedPropertyException Specialized JsonMappingException sub-class specifically used to indicate problems due to encountering a JSON property that could not be mapped to an Object property (via getter, constructor argument or field).
